name: I Thee Wed: Modern Wedding Project Life Journaling Card Set with Sentiment Cut Outs for Photos
description:
This set of 17 journaling cards is perfect for your DIY Project Life wedding album. The included cut-outs are also perfect for placing on top of your favorite pictures, after all, the wedding should be all about the memories! Write down your proposal story, how the rehearsal dinner went, your vows, anything you want to add!

Sentiments on the ribbons range from generic "Mr. & Mrs." down to more specific things, like "Groomsmen," "Best Man," "The Dress," "The Shoes," etc. To give you freedom to add tons of pictures without taking away space for filler cards! A few of the sentiment ribbons are longer and will only fit on a horizontal 4x6 photo, the rest could be used for either layout. 

You get high resolution .jpegs of all 17 journaling cards, plus 6 printable .pdf pages. The Cut-Out Photo Sentiment Ribbons are only included as a full page .pdf printable.

Set includes:
5 - 3x4* Filler Cards 
7 - 3x4* Journaling Cards 
5 - 4x6 Journaling Cards
27 - 0.5" high x varying width Cut-out Photo Sentiment Ribbons

*in order to fit in the page protectors for Project Life, the cards are actually sized at 2.9 x 4

These journaling cards are for personal use only. No physical product will be delivered to you. Your digital files will be delivered to your PayPal email address usually within 24 hours of purchase, after payment has been cleared.

name: Blank Journaling Cards, 3x4
description:
This set of 24 (yep, count 'em, 24!!) digital journaling cards will fit right in with your Project Life and other scrapbook or smashbook cards! They are generically colored to blend in with other sets and are included in both color and grayscale.

That's 24 cards you can use and reuse and repurpose and reprint as many times as you want!

You get high resolution .jpegs of all 24 journaling cards, plus 4 printable .pdf pages.

Set includes:
12 - 3x4 Journaling Cards in color
12 - 3x4 Journaling Cards in grayscale

**in order to fit in the page protectors for Project Life, the cards are actually sized at 2.9 x 4

These journaling cards are for personal use only. No physical product will be delivered to you. The link to download your digital files will be delivered to your PayPal email address usually within 24 hours of purchase, after payment has been cleared.
